import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}><MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"chatql"}}>{`ChatQL`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"push-notiifcation"}}>{`Push Notiifcation`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"email"}}>{`Email`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"store"}}>{`Store`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"social-feeds"}}>{`Social Feeds`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
